The mass funeral service of the 21 young people who died in the Enyobeni tavern tragedy is being held this morning. President Cyril Ramaphosa will speak at the service at the Scenery Park Sports Grounds in East London in the Eastern Cape. The empty coffins of the victims will be taken to the venue, and burials will then be conducted privately by their families. LIVE STREAM:
